title: Perfect Little Girls
description:
The Powerpuff Girls might have been three perfect little girls, but Professor Utonium was far from perfect.

Performed at The Upright Citizen's Brigade Theater as part of Maude Night (1/12/15).
Written by: Nicole Conlan
Directed by: Ellena Chmielewski.
Shot by: Jordan Olds

Starring:
Ryan Farrell
Keith Kingbay
Bardia Salimi
Lauren Brickman
Christine Bullen
Audrey Standfield
